## BORDER CROSSING
We have just crossed from **{{.From}}** into **{{.To}}**.

### TASK
Announce this border crossing in a pithy, interesting way.
Your response MUST be under {{.MaxWords}} words.

### OUTPUT FORMAT
Respond ONLY with a JSON object containing the following fields:
- `title`: A short, descriptive title for this announcement (e.g. "Crossing into {{.To}}").
- `script`: The pithy narration text (max {{.MaxWords}} words). Use the language: {{.Language_name}} ({{.Language_code}}).

### EXAMPLE
{
  "title": "Crossing into France",
  "script": "Au revoir, Italy! We have just crossed the border and are now soaring over the beautiful landscape of France."
}

